---
description: Rules for rotor logic and encryption in the Enigma web app
globs: **/lib/rotors/**/*.{ts,js}
alwaysApply: true
---

- Each rotor must be a permutation of 64 integers (0–63).
- Encoding/decoding only works after the user sets a start position (1–64) for each rotor.
- Rotor logic must be pure and testable — no side effects or direct DOM access.